A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F31191119%2Fzomato.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20rights-based%20laws%20passed%20recently%20in%20Rajasthan%20have%20received%20nation-wide%20attention.%20While%20most%20are%20well-intentioned%20and%20progressive%2C%20some%20may%20call%20for%20improvement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Bill%20passed%20in%20July%2C%202023%20gives%20the%20right%20to%20125%20days%20of%20employment%20to%20those%20who%20can%20work.%20Those%20unable%20to%20work%20have%20been%20ensured%20a%20pension.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%20is%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20bring%20a%20law%20that%20has%20an%20enhanced%20entitlement%20of%2025%20days%20for%20work%20under%20MGNREGA%20at%20its%20own%20cost.%20While%20many%20states%20have%20urban%20employment%20guarantee%20schemes%2C%20Rajasthan%20is%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20provide%20a%20legal%20entitlement%20of%20125%20days%20of%20work%20under%20an%20urban%20employment%20programme%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEmployment%20guarantee%20and%20income%20guarantee%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Bill%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20tackle%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20crisis.%20The%20bill%20emphasises%20that%20providing%20employment%20with%20decent%20wages%20to%20all%20who%20seek%20work%20should%20be%20the%20means%20of%20ensuring%20minimum%20income.%20This%20is%20important%20especially%20since%20there%20is%20so%20much%20work%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20in%20the%20country%20for%20which%20lack%20of%20funds%20is%20always%20given%20as%20an%20excuse.%20The%20gap%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20vast%2C%20idle%20workforce%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20work%20needed%20to%20be%20done%20in%20the%20country%20was%20first%20pointed%20out%20by%20Swedish%20economist%20Gunnar%20Myrdal%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEmpowering%20women%20with%20employment%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20the%20situation%20of%20women.%20Their%20work%20participation%20rates%20are%20declining%20but%20their%20burden%20of%20unpaid%20family%20labour%20is%20rising.%20Hence%2C%20there%20is%20the%20demand%20to%20convert%20unpaid%20care%20work%20of%20women%20in%20the%20household%20to%20paid%20work%20%E2%80%93%20providing%20elderly%20care%2C%20child%20care%20and%20care%20of%20the%20physically%20challenged%20%E2%80%93%20through%20self-help%20groups%20of%20women%20would%20be%20a%20better%20way%20of%20giving%20them%20economic%20independence%20and%20thus%20empowering%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEnsuring%20genuine%20development%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEmployment%20for%20both%20men%20and%20women%20could%20also%20be%20in%20terms%20of%20ensuring%20ecological%20sustainability%20through%20afforestation%2C%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20lake%20desilting%2C%20etc.%3B%20providing%20social%20infrastructure%20in%20terms%20of%20decent%20anganwadis%2C%20schools%2C%20primary%20healthcare%20centres%2C%20low-income%20social%20housing%2C%20etc.%2C%20which%20are%20being%20neglected%20right%20now%20due%20to%20the%20penchant%20for%20airports%2C%20bullet%20trains%2C%20expressways%2C%20and%20so%20on%20as%20the%20markers%20of%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99.%20All%20the%20above-mentioned%20works%20for%20empowering%20women%2C%20for%20ecological%20sustainability%20and%20required%20social%20infrastructure%20can%20be%20accommodated%20within%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20employment%20guarantee%20provisions%20leading%20to%20genuine%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERight%20to%20work%20for%20every%20adult%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Act%20says%20that%20the%20Right%20to%20Work%20under%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Income%20Guarantee%20Act%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20for%20%E2%80%98every%20adult%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20for%20only%20one%20person%20per%20household%20as%20in%20the%20MGNREGA.%20This%20is%20a%20remarkable%20change%20indeed%20if%20the%20necessary%20resources%20for%20this%20have%20been%20truly%20estimated%20and%20ensured.%20The%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20is%20a%20historic%20fulfilment%20of%20many%20of%20the%20demands%20that%20the%20citizens%E2%80%99%20movements%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Right%20to%20Work%20Campaign%2C%20Pension%20Parishad%20and%20the%20Soochna%20Evum%20Rozgar%20Adhikar%20Abhiyan%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20advocating%20for%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMinimum%20pension%20to%20those%20unable%20to%20work%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Pension%20Parishad%20in%202009%2C%20it%20has%20been%20campaigning%20through%20continual%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edharnas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(sit-ins)%20for%20a%20legal%20entitlement%20for%20pension%20that%20is%20universal%2C%20indexed%20to%20inflation%20and%20amounting%20to%20half%20the%20minimum%20wage.%20The%20indifference%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20elderly%20and%20these%20demands%20from%20citizens%E2%80%99%20groups%20has%20been%20evident%20with%20the%20allocation%20to%20the%20National%20Social%20Assistance%20Programme%20being%20limited%20to%20Rs%20200%20per%20month%20for%20BPL%20families%20since%202007.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Act%20makes%20Rajasthan%20the%20first%20state%20to%20guarantee%20by%20law%20a%20minimum%20pension%2C%20which%20also%20doubles%20the%20minimum%20pension%20to%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20for%20all%20eligible%20elderly%2C%20widowed%20and%20disabled%2C%20with%20a%20guaranteed%20annual%20increment%20of%2015%25%20per%20year.%20These%20provisions%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20new%20law%20have%20given%20effect%20to%20the%20decades-long%20demand%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20campaign%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHar%20haath%20ko%20kaam%20do%2C%20kaam%20ka%20poora%20daam%20do%3B%20budhaape%20me%20aaram%20do%2C%20pension%20aur%20samman%20do%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(guarantee%20employment%20for%20everyone%2C%20ensure%20minimum%20wage%20for%20those%20employed%20and%20ensure%20well-being%20of%20the%20elderly%20after%20retirement%20through%20pension)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20Pension%20Parishad%20that%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20pension%20to%20all%20elderly%2C%20widowed%20and%20disabled%20is%20being%20guaranteed%20by%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20law%2C%20the%20recently%20passed%20legislation%20says%20that%20pension%20to%20the%20elderly%20will%20be%20paid%20to%20only%20%E2%80%98eligible%20persons%E2%80%99%20and%20not%20universally.%20The%20eligibility%20criteria%20are%20still%20to%20be%20detailed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESecuring%20universal%20pensions%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20noted%20that%2C%20as%20far%20as%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20pensions%20are%20concerned%2C%20all%20developed%20welfare%20states%20achieve%20that%20by%20combining%20tax-based%20social%20assistance%20to%20those%20who%20cannot%20contribute%20towards%20their%20pensions%20(as%20in%20the%20law%20passed%20by%20Rajasthan)%2C%20with%20compulsory%20contributions%2C%20by%20workers%20who%20are%20able%20to%20pay%20during%20their%20working%20years%2C%20and%20by%20employers%20and%20the%20government.%20Nowhere%20is%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20pension%20to%20cover%20all%20elderly%20ensured%20without%20any%20contributions%20from%20workers%2C%20employers%20and%20the%20government%20towards%20it.%20Any%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98universalising%E2%80%99%20pensions%20without%20ensuring%20some%20contributions%20would%20make%20it%20unsustainable%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUnorganised%20workers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20Unorganised%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Social%20Security%20(UWSS)%20Act%20of%202008%20was%20supposed%20to%20find%20a%20way%20of%20providing%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20social%20security%20benefits%20to%20every%20unorganised%20worker.%20But%20it%20has%20fallen%20by%20the%20wayside%20after%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20as%20it%20did%20not%20clarify%20within%20the%20law%20what%20social%20security%20benefits%20it%20would%20guarantee%2C%20what%20their%20quantum%20would%20be%2C%20how%20the%20resources%20for%20it%20would%20be%20sourced%20from%20workers%2C%20employers%20and%20government%2C%20how%20it%20would%20be%20delivered%20and%20who%20would%20be%20exempted%20from%20contributions.%20The%20UWSS%20Act%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20by%20the%20Social%20Security%20Code%20of%202020%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20notified%20for%20implementation%20as%20states%20are%20still%20framing%20the%20rules%20under%20it.%20But%20this%20Code%20too%20has%20repeated%20all%20the%20above%20failings%20of%20the%20UWSS%20Act%20as%20far%20as%20unorganised%20workers%20are%20concerned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EILO%20Convention%20102%20on%20Social%20Security%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECuriously%2C%20the%20campaigns%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%20social%20security%20have%20been%20limited%20to%20demanding%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20pension%20and%20have%20overlooked%20the%20eight%20other%20social%20security%20benefits%20like%20medical%20care%20and%20sickness%2C%20unemployment%2C%20employment%20injury%2C%20family%2C%20maternity%2C%20invalidity%20and%20survivors%E2%80%99%20benefits%20as%20per%20ILO%20Convention%20102.%20The%20International%20Labour%20Organisation%20(ILO)%20Convention%20102%20sets%20out%20minimum%20standards%20for%20the%20level%20of%20social%20security%20benefits%20and%20the%20conditions%20under%20which%20they%20are%20to%20be%20granted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20partial%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20above%20necessity%20of%20having%20total%20social%20security%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Assembly%20has%20also%20passed%20the%20sector-specific%20Rajasthan%20Platform-Based%20Gig%20Workers%20(Registration%20and%20Welfare)%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20pass%20a%20legislation%20ensuring%20social%20security%20to%20platform-based%20gig%20workers.%20The%20key%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20include%3A%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20tripartite%20board%20with%20the%20representation%20of%20aggregators%2C%20workers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20and%20government%20with%20the%20powers%20to%20register%20platform-based%20gig%20workers%20in%20the%20state%2C%20notify%20and%20administer%20social%20security%20schemes%20for%20them%2C%20and%20monitor%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Act.%20It%20also%20introduces%20a%20dedicated%20welfare%20cess%20fee%20on%20each%20bill%20generated%20by%20the%20aggregator%20to%20the%20customer.%20The%20fee%20collected%20from%20individual%20transactions%20will%20be%20credited%20to%20a%20social%20security%20fund%20which%20would%20be%20used%20towards%20financing%20schemes%20meant%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20platform-based%20gig%20workers.%20This%20proposed%20mechanism%20in%20the%20gig-workers%E2%80%99%20Act%20has%20drawn%20inspiration%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ilo.org%2Fdyn%2Fnatlex%2Fdocs%2FELECTRONIC%2F17861%2F110575%2FF-1301927122%2FIND17861.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMaharashtra%20Mathadi%20Hamal%20and%20other%20Manual%20Workers%20Act%2C%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fhandle%2F123456789%2F1989%3Fsam_handle%3D123456789%2F1362%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBuilding%20and%20other%20Construction%20Workers%20Welfare%20Act%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Act%20is%20not%20the%20only%20law%20to%20recognise%20the%20needs%20of%20gig%20workers.%20The%20Social%20Security%20Code%20passed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%202020%20too%20recognises%20gig%20workers%20including%20platform%20workers.%20It%20has%20provided%20for%20a%20Board%20and%20similar%20mechanisms%20for%20registering%20all%20workers%20and%20aggregators%2C%20framing%20of%20social%20security%20schemes%2C%20establishing%20a%20social%20security%20fund%20and%20imposing%20an%20obligation%20on%20the%20gig%20employers%20to%20contribute%201-2%25%20of%20their%20annual%20turnover%20into%20the%20Fund%2C%20to%20be%20used%20for%20carrying%20out%20the%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESoochna%20Evam%20Rozgar%20Abhiyan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20involved%20with%20the%20advocacy%20and%20drafting%20of%20the%20Rajasthan%20gig-workers%E2%80%99%20Bill%2C%20recommends%20enacting%20similar%20%E2%80%98sector-specific%20Boards%E2%80%99%20for%20ensuring%20%E2%80%98specific%20rights%20and%20schemes%E2%80%99%20for%20all%20unorganised%20workers%20in%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20will%20mean%20that%20workers%20of%20specific%20sectors%20will%20get%20varied%20and%20piecemeal%20benefits%20under%20various%20boards%20and%20not%20universal%20coverage%20or%20uniform%20benefits%2C%20which%20is%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20several%20already%20existing%20schemes.%20One%20wonders%20how%20many%20sector-specific%20boards%20will%20be%20required%20to%20cover%20all%20unorganised%20sector%20workers%20who%20constitute%2093%25%20of%20the%20labour%20force%20and%20what%20the%20administrative%20cost%20of%20such%20a%20measure%20would%20be.%20The%20Mathadi%20workers%E2%80%99%20board%20for%20instance%20is%20catering%20to%20about%20one%20lakh%20workers%20only.%20One%20needs%20to%20note%20that%20Kerala%2C%20which%20has%20around%2012%20such%20Boards%2C%20has%20been%20restructuring%20them%20to%20avoid%20duplications%20in%20membership%20and%20provide%20standard%20benefits%20to%20all%20members.%20It%20is%20being%20admitted%20that%20the%20huge%20establishment%20costs%20of%20multiple%20boards%20are%20a%20problem%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20avoid%20the%20hazards%20of%20having%20a%20multiplicity%20of%20boards%2C%20the%20second%20National%20Commission%20on%20Labour%20(NCL)%20suggested%20astutely%20that%20%E2%80%9Carea-based%20schemes%20appear%20to%20be%20eminently%20suitable%20for%20application%20to%20the%20workers%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector%2C%20who%20are%20too%20numerous%20to%20be%20covered%20under%20occupation-based%20schemes%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20earlier%20and%20better%20version%20of%20the%20SSC%20too%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Infrastructure%20of%20local%20bodies%20(i.e.%20panchayats%20and%20municipal%20bodies)%20can%20be%20used%20for%20providing%20registration%20of%20both%20workers%20and%20entities%2C%20grievance%20redressal%20services%20%E2%80%A6.%20and%20in%20administration%20of%20the%20social%20security%20system%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ILO%20too%20had%20recommended%20an%20area-based%20approach%20rather%20than%20a%20sector-specific%20approach%20for%20providing%20social%20security%20to%20unorganised%20workers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EShifting%20sectors%20of%20unorganised%20workers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20reason%20for%20abjuring%20sector-specific%20boards%20would%20be%20because%20unorganised%20workers%20often%20shift%20from%20one%20sector%20to%20another.%20Agriculture%20workers%20from%20rural%20areas%20often%20transmute%20into%20construction%20workers%20in%20urban%20areas%20when%20seasonal%20farm%20work%20ends.%20Restrictions%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20one%20specifying%20that%20a%20worker%20should%20have%20worked%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%2090%20days%20to%20be%20registered%20and%20obtain%20benefits%20under%20the%20Building%20%26amp%3B%20Other%20Construction%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Board%20%E2%80%93%20often%20act%20as%20a%20hindrance%20to%20the%20worker%20being%20eligible%20under%20any%20Board.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaking%20coverage%20universal%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20is%20why%20these%20measures%20are%20being%20introduced%20in%20piecemeal%20fashion%20covering%20particular%20sectors%20of%20employment%20and%20for%20certain%20rights%20only%20and%20not%20being%20extended%20to%20cover%20all%20unorganised%20workers%20and%20all%20nine%20benefits%20to%20%E2%80%98universalise%E2%80%99%20social%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Advisory%20Council%20during%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20had%20suggested%20a%20clear%20and%20unambiguous%20exclusion%20criteria%20for%20ensuring%20universal%20coverage%20of%20unorganised%20workers%20for%20social%20security.%20Only%20two%20categories%20of%20workers%20were%20to%20be%20excluded%3A%20(i)%20workers%20already%20covered%20by%20the%20existing%20PF%20and%20ESIC%20schemes%3B%20and%20(ii)%20self-employed%20and%20other%20workers%20who%20pay%20income%20tax%20and%20are%20relatively%20better-off.%20All%20others%20were%20to%20be%20covered%2C%20without%20restrictions%20on%20sectors%2C%20limits%20on%20wages%20and%20number%20of%20workers%20in%20an%20establishment%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20provision%20stating%20that%20certain%20employers%20may%20pay%20as%20their%20contribution%20a%20percentage%20of%20their%20annual%20turnover%2C%20or%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20wages%20paid%20by%20them%20in%20a%20year%20to%20their%20unorganised%20workers%2C%20and%20file%20returns%20annually%20should%20have%20been%20the%20mode%20prescribed%20for%20all%20informal%2Funorganised%20sector%20employers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Unorganised%20Workers%20Welfare%20(MP)%20Act%20of%202003%20mandates%20all%20registered%20employers%20to%20pay%205%25%20of%20the%20wages%20paid%20by%20them%20to%20their%20unorganised%20workers%2C%20however%2C%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGovernment%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20through%20cess%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MP%20Act%20also%20mandates%20cesses%20on%20various%20state-level%20taxes%20and%20royalties%20to%20provide%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20the%20single%20Social%20Security%20Fund%20(SSF)%3A%20an%20additional%20duty%20on%20transfer%20of%20property%3B%20additional%20tax%20on%20certain%20motor%20vehicles%3B%20a%20welfare%20cess%20on%20sale%20or%20supply%20of%20forest%20produce%3B%20royalty%20on%20certain%20minor%20minerals%3B%20welfare%20cess%20on%20notified%20agricultural%20produce.%20This%20was%20also%20a%20recommendation%20of%20CIVIC%20in%20an%20alternative%20Bill%20for%20unorganised%20workers%E2%80%99%20social%20security%20that%20it%20had%20prepared%20through%20a%20consultative%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESingle%20social%20security%20authority%20and%20fund%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20earlier%20version%20of%20the%20Social%20Security%20Code%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20attempted%20to%20rationalise%20all%20separate%20schemes%2C%20laws%20and%20boards%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20single%20Social%20Security%20Authority%20at%20the%20Union%20government%20level%20with%20state-level%20Boards%20and%20a%20single%20SSF.%20This%20was%20the%20format%20suggested%20even%20by%20the%20Labour%20Law%20Association%2C%20a%20non-governmental%20independent%20body.%20However%2C%20the%20latest%20SS%20Code%20version%20fails%20in%20this.%20The%20Arjun%20Sengupta%20Commission%20had%20recommended%20just%20two%20Boards%2C%20one%20for%20wage-workers%20and%20one%20for%20the%20self-employed.%20The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Act%20has%20also%20formed%20just%20two%20Boards%3A%20one%20for%20rural%20and%20one%20for%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHopefully%2C%20a%20citizens%E2%80%99%20movement%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20to%20include%20a%20means%20of%20securing%20compulsory%20contributions%20to%20fund%20social%20security%20for%20unorganised%20workers%20through%20amendments%20to%20SSC%2C%20which%20currently%20says%20nothing%20about%20it.%20Or%20a%20completely%20new%20Bill%20for%20unorganised%20workers%E2%80%99%20social%20security%2C%20will%20have%20to%20be%20drafted%20asking%20merely%20for%20the%20extension%20of%20Employees%E2%80%99%20State%20Insurance%20(ESI)%20and%20Employees%20Provident%20Fund%20(EPF)%20to%20unorganised%20workers%20may%20result%20in%20difficulties%20in%20implementation%20as%20those%20are%20not%20geared%20to%20suit%20the%20particular%20working%20conditions%20of%20unorganised%20workers.%20This%20is%20a%20long-overdue%20Bill%20needed%20to%20universalise%20social%20security%20for%20the%20crores%20of%20unorganised%20workers%20working%20under%20precarious%20conditions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20author%20is%20the%20Executive%20Trustee%20of%20CIVIC-Bangalore%20and%20a%20life-member%20of%20the%20Social%20Security%20Association%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691584222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F31191119%2Fzomato.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Frajasthans-rights-based-laws-hits-and-misses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20attempt%20at%20%E2%80%98universalising%E2%80%99%20pensions%20without%20ensuring%20some%20contributions%20from%20workers%2C%20employers%20and%20the%20government%20would%20make%20it%20unsustainable%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen