%20House%20has%20also%20urged%20the%20Centre%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20amend%20the%20name%20under%20Article%203%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20states%20as%20well%20as%20any%20changes%20to%20the%20names%20or%20areas%20of%20existing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETabling%20the%20resolution%20today%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20name%20of%20our%20state%20is%20Keralam%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20language.%20States%20were%20formed%20based%20on%20language%20on%20November%201%2C%201956.%20Kerala%20Day%20is%20also%20on%20November%201.%20The%20need%20to%20unite%20Kerala%20for%20the%20Malayalam-speaking%20communities%20has%20been%20strongly%20evident%20since%20the%20time%20of%20the%20national%20freedom%20struggle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20name%20of%20our%20state%20is%20listed%20as%20Kerala%20in%20the%20First%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20Assembly%20unanimously%20requests%20the%20Union%20Government%20to%20take%20immediate%20steps%20to%20amend%20it%20to%20'Keralam'%20under%20Article%203%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20House%20also%20requests%20that%20our%20state%20be%20renamed%20as%20'Keralam'%20in%20all%20the%20languages%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Eighth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20First%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20lists%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20and%20their%20territorial%20jurisdictions%2C%20while%20the%20Eighth%20Schedule%20lists%20the%2022%20official%20languages%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20opposition%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20alliance%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20did%20not%20suggest%20any%20amendments%20to%20it.%20Based%20on%20a%20show%20of%20hands%2C%20the%20resolution%20was%20then%20declared%20as%20unanimously%20adopted%20by%20Speaker%20AN%20Shamseer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20informed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20it%20had%20given%20its%20approval%20for%20the%20renaming%20of%20seven%20cities%20and%20towns%20-%20including%20Allahabad%20to%20Prayagraj%20-%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20received%20a%20proposal%20from%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20to%20rename%20the%20state%20as%20'Bangla'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20cities%20and%20towns%20can%20be%20changed%20by%20states%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20but%20changing%20a%20state's%20name%20requires%20the%20Parliament's%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Kerala%20has%20reverted%20to%20the%20original%20names%20for%20many%20of%20its%20towns%20and%20cities%2C%20including%20the%20capital%20Trivandrum%2C%20which%20is%20now%20called%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20Cochin%20went%20back%20to%20the%20traditional%20Kochi%2C%20Quilon%20to%20Kollam%20and%20Trichur%20to%20Thrissur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691583900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2F1o6ej8f_kerala-generic-pixabay-650_625x300_31_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-new-name-keralam-live-updates-gods-own-country-may-not-be-called-kerala-soon-details-here-4283285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22God's%20Own%20Country%20may%20soon%20get%20a%20new%20name.A%20resolution%20moved%20by%20the%20Kerala%20chief%20minister%20to%20rename%20the%20state%20'Keralam'%2C%20which%20is%20what%20it%20is%20called%20in%20Malayalam%2C%20has%20been%20passed%20unanimously%20by%20the%20Assembly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-new-name-keralam-live-updates-gods-own-country-may-not-be-called-kerala-soon-detai