nfidence%20motion%20moved%20by%20the%20opposition.%20Here%20are%20Mr%20Shah's%20top%20quotes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESometimes%20in%20order%20to%20check%20the%20government's%20majority%2C%20the%20opposition%20brings%20the%20no-confidence%20motion.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20house%20have%20full%20confidence%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Whenever%20you%20bring%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%2C%20you%20bring%20arguments%20over%20the%20policies%20and%20decisions.%20It%20was%20brought%20only%20for%20%3Cem%3Ekranti%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20no-trust%20motion%20was%20brought%20to%20mislead%20people.%20The%20house%20and%20the%20people%20have%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20want%20to%20tell%20everyone%20that%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20is%20the%20first%20government%20since%20independence%20with%20two-third%20majority%2C%20and%20the%20confidence%20of%20people%20did%20that%2C%20twice.%20PM%20Modi%20is%20the%20hardest%20working%20PM%20since%20independence.%20Many%20surveys%20in%20the%20world%20say%20that%20too.%20He%20has%20never%20taken%20leave%2C%20he%20works%20for%2017%20hours%20a%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPM%20Modi%20gave%20the%20slogan%20-%20Corruption%20quit%20India%2C%20dynastic%20politics%20quit%20India%2C%20appeasement%20quit%20India.%20The%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20a%20constitutional%20process%2C%20and%20we%20have%20no%20objection.%20I%20believe%20it%20brings%20out%20the%20real%20face%20of%20alliances.%20When%20Narasimha%20Rao%20was%20in%20power%2C%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20brought%20and%20the%20Congress%20wanted%20to%20save%20the%20government.%20They%20won%20the%20motion%20and%20sent%20many%20political%20leaders%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECongress%20had%20been%20in%20power%20for%2035%20years%3B%20they%20took%20many%20decisions%20that%20will%20be%20remembered.%20But%20in%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20over%2050%20decisions%20had%20been%20taken%2C%20which%20will%20also%20be%20remembered.%20For%2030%20years%2C%20the%20country%20had%20been%20suffering%20from%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20corruption%2C%20and%20casteism%20and%20PM%20Modi%20finished%20all%20these%20and%20gave%20politics%20of%20performance%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%201999%2C%20during%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20government%2C%20we%20could%20have%20also%20done%20that%20(bribing%20leaders)%20and%20we%20put%20forward%20our%20points%20and%20lost%20the%20motion%20by%20one%20vote%2C%20we%20could%20have%20saved%20the%20motion.%20Sometimes%2C%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20brings%20out%20the%20real%20pic%20of%20alliances.%20We%20lost%20by%20one%20vote%20but%20came%20back%20with%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPeople%20are%20watching%2C%20and%20they%20know%20everything.%20We%20are%20in%20politics%20of%20development%2C%20but%20they%20bribe%20leaders%20to%20save%20their%20government%20and%20principles.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20(Congress)%20waived%20off%20loans%20worth%20Rs%2070%2C000%20crore.%20We%20don't%20believe%20in%20waving%20off%20loans.%20We%20want%20people%20to%20not%20take%20loans%20and%20give%20them%20benefits%20through%20the%20direct%20transfer%20benefit%20scheme.%20This%20is%20not%20revdi%20(freebies).%20We%20did%20a%20survey%20and%20gave%20Rs%206%2C000%20to%20farmers%20who%20own%20less%20than%202.5%20acre%20land.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E(Bihar%20Chief%20Minister)%20Nitish%20Kumar%20made%20fun%20of%20Jan%20Dhan%20scheme.%20We%20opened%2049.65%20crore%20bank%20accounts%20and%20used%20direct-benefit%20transfer%20(DBT).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20was%20able%20to%20successfully%20fight%20COVD-19%3B%20the%20centre%20and%20state%20governments%20fought%20the%20pandemic%20together.%20But%20the%20opposition%20targeted%20the%20government%20over%20vaccine%20and%20called%20it%20'Modi%20vaccine'.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20may%20have%20no-confidence%20in%20the%20government%2C%20but%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20are%20with%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691583180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fbgnugmpg_amit-shah_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-quotes-amit-shah-in-parliament-on-no-confidence-motion-4283284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20spoke%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20on%20the%20discussion%20on%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20moved%20by%20the%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-quotes-amit-shah-in-parliament-on-no-confidence-motion-4283284%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-quotes-amit-shah-in-parliament-on-no-confidence-motion-4283284%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftop-quotes-amit-shah-in-parliament-on-no-confidence-motion-4283284%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kiara%20Advani%20reacts%20to%20'Don%203'%20teaser%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691582850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102575794%2Cimgsize-27052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkiara-advani-reacts-to-don-3-teaser-fans-speculate-if-actress-confirmed-her-role-opposite-ranveer-singh%2Farticleshow%2F102575772.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102575772.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKiara%20Advani%20is%20touted%20to%20be%20offered%20'Don%203'.%20The%20actress%20was%20at%20Farhan%20Akhtar's%20office%20yesterday%20and%20it%20was%20for%20'Don%203'%20in%20all%20likeliness.%20Her%20last%20release%20was%20'Satyaprem%20Ki%20Katha'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkiara-advani-reacts-to-don-3-teaser-fans-speculate-if-actress-confirmed-her-role-opposite-ranveer-singh%2Farticleshow%2F102575772.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20Bhatt%20fangirls%20over%20Gal%20Gadot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691582843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102574555%2Cimgsize-80498.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Falia-bhatt-fangirls-over-gal-gadot-recalls-time-when-wonder-woman-made-her-coffee%2Farticleshow%2F102574588.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102574588.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlia%20Bhatt%20expressed%20her%20admiration%20for%20her%20co-star%2C%20Gal%20Gadot%2C%20and%20recalled%20the%20time%20when%20the%20Wonder%20Woman%20actress%20made%20her%20coffee.%20Alia%20revealed%20that%20despite%20being%20a%20massive%20star%2C%20Gal%20was%20very%20humble%20and%20made%20them%20feel%20at%20home%20while%20shooting%20for%20the%20film.%20Gal%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20expressed%20her%20love%20and%20admiration%20for%20Alia%2C%20citing%20their%20connection%20and%20the%20Desi%20beauty's%20warmth%20as%20what%20made%20her%20stand%20out.%20'Heart%20Of%20Stone'%2C%20starring%20Alia%20Bhatt%2C%20Gal%20Gadot%2C%20and%20Jamie%20Dornan%2C%20will%20debut%20on%20Netflix%20on%20August%2011.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20War%20Lies%20Ahead%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20He%20Must%20Prepare%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F22162521%2FIMG_1705.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20won%20a%20battle%20on%20August%204.%20His%20political%20status%2C%20that%20of%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20able%20to%20contest%20elections%20at%20any%20level%2C%20had%20been%20taken%20away%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20he%20was%20convicted%20of%20defaming%20the%20Modi%20surname.%20From%20the%20conviction%20to%20the%20punishment%20to%20disqualification%2C%20politics%20was%20writ%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20mounted%20a%20vicious%20attack%20on%20PM%20Modi%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20February%2013.%20The%20BJP%20had%20already%20weaponised%20his%20comment%20during%20the%202019%20general%20election%20about%20%E2%80%9Call%20thieves%20carrying%20the%20Modi%20surname%E2%80%9D%20by%20making%20Purnesh%20Modi%2C%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20file%20a%20criminal%20defamation%20suit.%20The%20case%20opened%20in%20a%20Surat%20court%20on%20March%2023.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20awarded%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20%E2%80%93%20two%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20disqualification%20from%20contesting%20any%20polls%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20instantly%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20disqualified%20him%20on%20March%2024.%20The%20134-day%20politico-juridical%20offensive%20against%20him%20drew%20to%20a%20close%20on%20August%204%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stayed%20his%20conviction.%20On%20August%207%2C%20he%20was%20back%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Gandhi%20faces%20a%20much%20bigger%20war%20that%20would%20either%20establish%20him%20as%20a%20prime%20contender%20against%20the%20formidable%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20or%20reduce%20him%20to%20an%20also-ran.%20Aside%20from%20building%20his%20own%20party%2C%20which%20at%20the%20moment%20lies%20in%20tatters%2C%20stitching%20together%20an%20Opposition%20alliance%20before%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20could%20be%20his%20crowning%20glory.%20How%20capable%20is%20he%20of%20leading%20in%20the%20war%20ahead%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20Amethi%2C%20his%20family%20borough%2C%20returned%20him%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20A%20weak%20Congress%20party%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%201996%2C%20leading%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20with%20145%20seats.%20The%20UPA%20ran%20the%20government%20for%20a%20decade.%20Since%20then%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20chair%20of%20the%20National%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0(2007)%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20Indian%20Youth%20Congress%20(2007)%2C%20general%20secretary%20(2007-13)%2C%20vice%20president%20(2013-17)%20and%20president%20(2017-19)%20of%20his%20party.%20He%20was%20invited%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%20to%20join%20his%20cabinet%20in%202009%2C%20and%20the%20request%20was%20repeated%20in%202012.%20Not%20only%20did%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20not%20accept%2C%20his%20contribution%20to%20building%20his%20party%20during%20the%20decade%20when%20it%20held%20the%20reins%20of%20power%2C%20and%20when%20he%20was%20in%20various%20positions%20in%20the%20party%2C%20is%20negligible.%20In%20September%202013%2C%20he%20publicly%20insulted%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20by%20tearing%20up%20an%20ordinance%20and%20calling%20it%20nonsense.%20His%20action%20damaged%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20been%20in%20ideological%20drift%20since%20the%20second%20reign%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20(1980-84)%2C%20which%20was%20heightened%20when%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20helmed%20the%20party%20and%20the%20government.%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20and%20Sitaram%20Kesri%20did%20not%20contribute%20to%20party-building.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20understood%20the%20emerging%20coalition%20era%20and%20led%20the%20UPA%20to%20two%20terms%2C%20but%20could%20not%20build%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20competent%20to%20inject%20ideology%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%20into%20the%20drifting%20party%20during%20his%20two-year%20presidency.%20Taking%20the%20blame%20for%20the%202019%20defeat%2C%20he%20resigned%20the%20presidency.%20In%20the%2019th%20general%20election%20in%202019%2C%20he%20lost%20Amethi%20but%20won%20from%20Wayanad%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frahul-gandhi-parliament-bharat-mata-manipur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98You%20Are%20Anti-National%E2%80%99%3A%20In%20Parliament%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Says%20PM%20%E2%80%98Murdered%20Bharat%20Mata%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20he%20is%20not%20known%20for%20any%20meaningful%2C%20let%20alone%20brilliant%2C%20debate%20or%20intervention.%20He%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20PM%20in%20his%20speeches%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20but%20his%20oratory%20did%20not%20ever%20appear%20to%20be%20giving%20an%20alternative%20view%20or%20a%20vision%20regarding%20policies%20or%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecularism%20is%20a%20major%20victim%20of%20the%20right%20tilt%20of%20Indian%20politics%20since%202014.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20unclear%20on%20this%20issue.%20His%20soft%20Hindutva%20path%20has%20not%20yielded%20much%2C%20either%20for%20him%20or%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20remains%20his%20major%20political%20project.%20It%20improved%20his%20image%20and%20took%20him%20to%20the%20masses%20along%20the%20route.%20His%20smiling%20demeanour%2C%20simple%20clothing%20and%20accessibility%20despite%20the%20security%20cordon%20brought%20him%20goodwill%20along%20the%20route.%20It%20contributed%20to%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Karnataka.%20But%20the%20state%20is%20among%20the%20few%20where%20the%20party%20remains%20organisationally%20cohesive%2C%20with%20a%20local%20leadership.%20The%20yatra%20has%20not%20seen%20any%20follow-up%20party%20building%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20provoked%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20hastened%20action%20in%20the%20case%20about%20the%20comment%20on%20Modis%2C%20was%20critical%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20but%20bland%20about%20his%20yatra%20experience%20and%20any%20alternative%20vision%2C%20either%20of%20himself%20or%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20current%20political%20project%20is%20to%20bring%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20together%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%20He%20has%20done%20well%20to%20downplay%20both%20himself%20and%20his%20party%20to%20allay%20the%20fears%20of%2025%20other%20parties%20that%20joined%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EINDIA%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance).%20The%20imaginative%20name%20is%20said%20to%20be%20his%20contribution.%20Its%20acceptance%20by%20the%20alliance%20raises%20his%20stature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%2C%20however%2C%20only%20the%20beginning.%20Would%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20be%20able%20to%20help%20the%20alliance%20construct%20a%20more%20inclusive%20ideological%20platform%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20that%20have%20been%20deconstructed%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20in%20the%20past%20nine%20years%3F%20The%20programme%20and%20the%20manifesto%20would%20have%20to%20be%20substantively%20appealing%20to%20voters.%20The%20institutional%20and%20organisational%20issues%20relating%20to%20poll%20management%20across%20the%20country%20would%20need%20to%20be%20strengthened%20in%20the%20next%20nine%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20party%20and%20the%20Opposition%20camp%20rejoices%2C%20we%20wait%20and%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAjay%20K.%20Mehra%20is%20a%20political%20scientist.%20He%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21%20and%20Principal%2C%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Evening%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691582840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F22162521%2FIMG_1705.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-war-lies-ahead-of-rahul-gandhi-and-he-must-prepare%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Secularism%20is%20a%20major%20victim%20of%20the%20right%20tilt%20of%20Indian%20politics%20since%202014.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20unclear%20on%20this%20issue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-war-lies-ahead-of-rahul-gandhi-and-he-must-prepare%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22First-Time%20Locarno%20Contender%20Leonor%20Teles%20Questions%20Home%20and%20Love%20in%20%E2%80%98Baan%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98Sometimes%20We%20Need%20to%20Run%20Away%20to%20Come%20Back%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691582805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FBaan_5-Uma-Pedra-no-Sapato-2023.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235691823%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20belongs%20in%20two%20places%3A%20in%20love%20and%20at%20home.%20With%20her%20sophomore%20feature%2C%20Golden%20Leopard%20contender%20Leonor%20Teles%20questions%20the%20stability%20of%20both.%20%E2%80%9CBaan%E2%80%9D%20(Thai%20for%20home)%20reimagines%20the%20world%20of%20a%20lovelorn%20person%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20her%20own%20loneliness%20through%20a%20quasi-magical%20shift%20