yer%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Deverakonda%20and%20Samantha's%20much-awaited%20film%20%3Cem%3EKushi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20been%20in%20the%20news%20for%20all%20the%20right%20reasons%20ever%20since%20the%20first%20look%20of%20the%20film%20was%20released.%20After%20their%20first%20song%20%3Cem%3ENa%20Rojaa%20Nuvve%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20makers%20dropped%20yet%20another%20song%20titled%20%3Cem%3EAradhya%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20film%20last%20month.%20Talking%20about%20%3Cem%3EAradhya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Vijay%20Deverakonda%20shared%20that%20in%20some%20way%2C%20several%20moments%20in%20the%20song%20are%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20his%20life%20and%20experiences%26quot%3B%20even%20though%20he%20is%20not%20married.%20The%20actor%20also%20mentioned%20that%20he%20envisions%20his%20married%20life%20in%20a%20similar%20way.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20emotion%20captured%20by%20%3Cem%3EAradhya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Vijay%20Deverakonda%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAradhya%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20song%20if%20I%20try%20to%20tell%20it%20in%20one%20line%20-%20imagine%20a%20young%20couple%2C%20who%20is%20very%20much%20in%20love.%20They%20get%20married%20and%20it's%20that%20one%20year%20after%20marriage.%20That's%20beautiful%2C%20you%20have%20your%20own%20space%2C%20your%20own%20intimacy.%20You%20have%20all%20the%20time%20with%20this%20person%20you%20love.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20about%20that%20beautiful%20period%20post-marriage%2C%20usually%20before%20the%20shit%20hits%20the%20ceiling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20in%20some%20way%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20moments%20in%20the%20song%20are%20from%20my%20life%2C%20from%20the%20experiences%20that%20I%20have%20had.%20I%20am%20not%20married%20but%20in%20some%20sort%20of%20way%2C%20when%20I%20get%20married%20this%20is%20how%20I%20would%20like%20to%20see%20my%20married%20life%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWatch%20the%20full%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C