lash%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20advanced%20by%20a%20day%20to%20October%2014%20at%20Narendra%20Modi%20Stadium%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20ICC%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20schedule%20of%20eight%20other%20matches%20have%20also%20been%20changed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Findia-vs-pakistan-clash-now-on-october-14-as-icc-reschedules-nine-world-cup-fixtures%2Farticleshow%2F102575521.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Hugging%20Woman%20Without%20Sexual%20Intent%20Not%20An%20Offence%5C%22%3A%20Wrestling%20Body%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOutgoing%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20accused%20in%20a%20case%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20told%20a%20Delhi%20court%20that%20hugging%20or%20touching%20a%20woman%20without%20a%20sexual%20intent%20is%20not%20an%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20made%20the%20submissions%20before%20Additional%20Chief%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20Harjeet%20Singh%20Jaspal%20through%20his%20lawyer%20while%20opposing%20framing%20of%20charges%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20started%20hearing%20arguments%20on%20point%20of%20whether%20to%20frame%20the%20charges%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20and%20co-accused%20and%20suspended%20WFI%20assistant%20secretary%20Vinod%20Tomar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Rajiv%20Mohan%2C%20appearing%20for%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20further%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20allegations%20were%20time%20barred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20cosmetic%20grounds%20won't%20hold%20that%20I%20(complainant)%20was%20under%20threat.%20If%20you%20(complainants)%20are%20moving%20freely%20and%20for%20five%20years%20you%20did%20not%20come%20forward%20and%20then%20saying%20that%20you%20were%20under%20threat%20is%20not%20a%20valid%20explanation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20added%20that%20the%20court%20had%20no%20jurisdiction%20to%20try%20the%20case%20since%20the%20%26quot%3Boffences%20are%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20committed%20outside%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20take%20these%20allegations%2C%20Indian%20jurisdiction%20only%20lies%20in%20three%20of%20these%20allegations.%20The%20offences%20committed%20outside%20India%20cannot%20be%20tried%20by%20the%20court%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20sanction%20under.%20Two%20offences%20are%20related%20to%20Ashoka%20Road%20and%20Siri%20Fort.%20Offence%20at%20Siri%20Fort%20is%20only%20of%20hugging...%20Touching%20a%20woman%20without%20a%20criminal%20force%20or%20sexual%20intent%20is%20not%20an%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mohan%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bwrestling%20is%20such%20an%20event%2C%20mostly%20coaches%20are%20male.%20Female%20coaches%20are%20rare.%20If%20a%20coach%2C%20out%20of%20joy%2C%20after%20an%20achievement%2C%20is%20hugging%20a%20player%2C%20it%20can't%20fall%20under%20the%20category%20of%20offence...%20The%20event%20is%20such%20and%20if%20a%20male%20coach%20hugs%20a%20player%20out%20of%20anxiety%20is%20not%20an%20offence.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20continue%20to%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20metropolitan%20court%20had%20on%20July%2020%20granted%20bail%20to%20Mr%20Singh%20and%20Mr%20Tomar%20on%20a%20bond%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20each%20with%20certain%20conditions%2C%20including%20they%20shall%20not%20leave%20the%20country%20without%20the%20court's%20prior%20permission%20and%20not%20offer%20any%20inducement%20to%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20the%20six-time%20MP%20on%20June%2015%20under%20sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force