Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1768525%2Flegislative-spree-so-many-laws-so-little-time%5C%22%3Eseries%20of%20legislation%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0pushed%20through%20parliament%20in%20unprecedented%20haste%20just%20a%20few%20days%20before%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20has%20reinforced%20suspicions.%20Most%20alarming%20is%20the%20passage%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1768896%5C%22%3Eamendments%20to%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20sweeping%20powers%20to%20the%20security%20agencies%2C%20thus%20undermining%20civil%20rights.%20Although%20some%20of%20the%20provisions%20were%20slightly%20diluted%20after%20strong%20protest%20in%20the%20Senate%2C%20its%20overall%20lethality%20has%20not%20been%20blunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20unchecked%20powers%20for%20security%20agencies%20will%20further%20strengthen%20the%20extra-democratic%20forces.%20It%20seems%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20plan%20to%20silence%20the%20opposition.%20What%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20fails%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20it%20could%20also%20be%20used%20against%20them.%20It%20will%20certainly%20come%20back%20to%20haunt%20the%20current%20ruling%20parties.%20The%20shadow%20of%20the%20security%20establishment%20has%20already%20grown%20longer%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20country%20staying%20on%20the%20democratic%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20be%20moving%20towards%20permanent%20hybrid%20rule%2C%20with%20the%20civilians%20playing%20second%20fiddle.%20There%20are%20already%20signs%20of%20the%20security%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20creeping%20domination%2C%20with%20the%20security%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20increasing%20role%20in%20several%20civilian%20fields%2C%20including%20running%20the%20economy.%20The%20ruling%20coalition%20has%20virtually%20abdicated%20civilian%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20happening%20is%20a%20sad%20commentary%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20retreating%20democratic%20process%2C%20however%20weak%20it%20may%20have%20been%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20The%20last%2016%20months%20is%20a%20testimony%20to%20the%20backward%20march.%20The%20PTI%2C%20which%20is%20now%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20storm%2C%20is%20equally%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20to%20be%20blamed%20for%20wrecking%20the%20system%20with%20its%20destructive%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20taking%20the%20parliamentary%20path%2C%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%20took%20a%20confrontationist%20approach%2C%20seeking%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20entire%20edifice.%20His%20populist%20rhetoric%20and%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20disenchantment%20with%20the%20PDM%20government%20may%20have%20won%20him%20unprecedented%20support%20among%20the%20people%2C%20but%20his%20recklessness%20has%20done%20huge%20damage%20to%20the%20democratic%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20simultaneously%20took%20on%20his%20political%20rivals%20and%20erstwhile%20patrons%20in%20the%20security%20establishment.%20He%20is%20now%20paying%20the%20cost%20of%20his%20thoughtless%20populist%20politics.%20Though%20his%20popular%20base%20seems%20to%20have%20remained%20intact%2C%20the%20party%20is%20in%20disarray%2C%20with%20the%20departure%20of%20several%20leaders%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sign%20of%20Khan%20losing%20support%2C%20despite%20the%20restrictions%20on%20his%20statements%20being%20printed%20or%20telecast.%20In%20fact%2C%20his%20popularity%20graph%20seems%20to%20have%20climbed%20after%20his%20imprisonment.%20Despite%20state%20repression%20and%20efforts%20to%20dismantle%20the%20party%2C%20the%20PTI%20is%20still%20capable%20of%20giving%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20PML-N%20in%20the%20electoral%20battleground%20of%20Punjab%20even%20in%20relatively%20free%20polls.%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20the%20fear%20of%20being%20swept%20away%20that%20has%20brought%20the%20PDM%20closer%20to%20the%20security%20establishment%20and%20that%20has%20seen%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20new%20hybrid%20arrangement%20with%20another%20civilian%20partner.%20There%20is%20complete%20convergence%20between%20the%20two%20on%20eliminating%20the%20PTI%20challenge.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20it%20is%20democratic%20space%20that%20seems%20to%20be%20shrinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769178%2Fgovt-all-set-to-bow-out-after-premier-sends-advice-for-na-dissolution%5C%22%3EPDM%20government%E2%80%99s%20departure%20around%20the%20corner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20caretaker%20administration.%20With%20the%20PTI%2C%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20out%20of%20the%20consultation%20process%2C%20it%20has%20been%20left%20to%20the%20coalition%20partners%20and%20a%20token%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20to%20nominate%20the%20interim%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%94%20of%20course%2C%20with%20input%20from%20the%20security%20establishment.%20That%20would%20make%20the%20credentials%20of%20the%20interim%20government%20as%20a%20non-partisan%20body%20questionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20likelihood%20of%20prolonged%20interim%20rule%2C%20there%20is%20very%20much%20a%20possibility%20of%20an%20empowered%20technocratic%20setup%20being%20installed%20to%20run%20the%20administration%20during%20perhaps%20the%20most%20challenging%20time%20in%20our%20recent%20history.%20Such%20an%20arrangement%20would%20mean%20virtual%20military%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20such%20non-representative%20technocratic-cum-military%20rule%20stabilise%20the%20politically%20volatile%20situation%3F%20Of%20course%20not.%20Ruthless%20use%20of%20state%20power%20to%20suppress%20the%20opposition%20will%20only%20make%20things%20worse.%20It%20would%20then%20become%20extremely%20hard%20for%20anyone%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20dangerous%20scenario%20that%20confronts%20a%20country%20already%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20dire%20economic%20crisis%20and%20rising%20terrorism.%20Sidelining%20a%20popular%20leader%20and%20making%20and%20breaking%20political%20parties%20won%E2%80%99t%20stabilise%20the%20situation.%20Unfortunately%2C%20our%20political%20leadership%20has%20never%20leant%20any%20lesson%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20from%20their%20own%20history.%20The%20politics%20of%20confrontation%20and%20revenge%20has%20already%20led%20to%20shrinking%20democratic%20space.%20Delaying%20elections%20is%20not%20the%20solution.%20It%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20both%20the%20government%20and%20opposition%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20temperature%20in%20order%20to%20create%20a%20conducive%20atmosphere%20for%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20Regrettably%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20happening.%20The%20time%20for%20political%20reconciliation%20appears%20to%20be%20over.%20One%20can%20only%20hope%20sanity%20prevails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EZahid%20Hussain%20is%20an%20author%20and%20journalist.%20He%20tweets%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhidhussain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40hidhussain%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20email%20is%20zhussain100%40yahoo.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769194%5C%22%3EDAWN%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691580653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24214756%2FImran_Khan_Arif_Alvi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fin-pakistan-the-citizen-plays-second-fiddle%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20dangerous%20scenario%20that%20confronts%20a%20country%20already%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20dire%20economic%20crisis%20and%20rising%20terrorism.%20Sidelining%20a%20popular%20leader%20an