0cannot%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edesh%20bhakts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bpatriotic%5D%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20you%20cannot%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edesh%20premi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20You%20have%20murdered%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20added%20that%20this%20is%20why%20Modi%20has%20not%20visited%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20PM%20does%20not%20go%20to%20Manipur%20because%20you%20have%20murdered%20India%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20not%20the%20protectors%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%2C%20you%20are%20the%20murderers%20of%20Bharat%20Mata%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Loud%20protests%20broke%20out%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20a%20frequent%20occurrence%20while%20Gandhi%20spoke.%20%3C%2Fspan%3ECongress%20MPs%20could%20be%20heard%20telling%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20that%20they%20too%20will%20start%20interrupting%20when%20BJP%20MPs%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20tweeted%20that%20Sansad%20TV%20showed%20Gandhi%20for%20less%20than%2040%25%20of%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20first%20speech%20after%20coming%20back%20from%20the%20unjustified%20disqualification%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20spoke%20from%2012%3A09pm%20to%2012%3A46pm%20i.e.%2037%20minutes%20during%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20which%20the%20Sansad%20TV%20camera%20showed%20him%20for%20ONLY%2014%20mins%2037%20seconds.%20That%E2%80%99s%20less%20than%2040%25%20screen%20time!%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fr8AHVHdNGv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fr8AHVH