%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20the%20Kerala%20Assembly%20resoundingly%20passed%20a%20resolution%20against%20the%20Union%20Government%E2%80%99s%20unilateral%20and%20hasty%20move%20to%20impose%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUniformCivilCode%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23UniformCivilCode%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20UCC%20without%20engaging%20in%20democratic%20debate%20or%20seeking%20consensus%20poses%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20the%20unity%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzFk4pn7fWH%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzFk4pn7fWH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20(%40pinarayivijayan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpinarayivijayan%2Fstatus%2F1688843293088780288%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20was%20moved%20by%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20and%20was%20backed%20by%20both%20the%20ruling%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20and%20the%20opposition%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20that%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20come%20forward%20with%20a%20unilateral%20move%20to%20implement%20UCC%20without%20taking%20any%20attempt%20to%20create%20a%20consensus%20over%20the%20issue%20among%20the%20different%20segments%20of%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20according%20to%20the%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20a%20UCC%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdetrimental%20to%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20opposition%20parties%20and%20civil%20society%20actors%20have%20alleged%20that%20th