id%20that%20the%3Cspan%3E%20ethnic%20conflict%20in%20Manipur%20threatens%20not%20just%20to%20tear%20apart%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20state%20but%20calls%20into%20question%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20spirit%20of%20harmony%20and%20fraternity%20that%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98unity%20in%20diversity%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open%20statement%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%3EConstitutional%20Conduct%20Group%20(CCG)%2C%20released%20on%20August%206%2C%20is%20signed%20by%20more%20than%20100%20former%20civil%20servants.%20It%20accused%20the%20Manipur%20state%20government%20and%20the%20state%20police%20of%20dereliction%20of%20their%20fundamental%20duty%20to%20protect%20the%20life%20and%20property%20of%20citizens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20with%20a%20deliberately%20orchestrated%20and%20targeted%20carnage%20that%20has%20included%20large%20scale%20arson%2C%20lynching%2C%20collective%20rape%2C%20vandalism%2C%20looting%2C%20mob%20violence%20and%20obstruction%20of%20central%20security%20forces%20from%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties%2C%20followed%20by%20armed%20attacks%20and%20retaliation%20by%20both%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Ctotal%20failure%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20state%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20raiding%20of%20police%20armouries%2C%20which%20has%20allowed%20people%20to%20loot%20around%204%2C500%20weapons%20and%20an%20estimated%205%20lakh%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%2C%20the%20statement%20says.%20Such%20looting%20is%20unimaginable%20and%20without%20precedent%20in%20India%2C%20the%20signatories%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20priority%E2%80%9D%20must%20be%20to%20provide%20a%20healing%20touch%20through%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20measures%2C%20compensation%20and%20other%20assistance%2C%20CCG%20said.%20The%20statement%20adds%20that%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20%E2%80%9Cu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enderlying%20causes%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20conflict%20%E2%80%9Cneed%20to%20be%20objectively%20identified%20and%20addressed%20within%20the%20bounds%20of%20constitutional%20parameters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20civil%20servants%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20i%3C%2Fspan%3Empose%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20Manipur%3B%20p%3Cspan%3Erovide%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20measures%3B%20and%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eake%20severe%20punitive%20action%20against%20individuals%20and%20groups%20intent%20on%20fomenting%20unrest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full%20statement%20and%20the%20list%20of%20signatories%20are%20reproduced%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECCG%20OPEN%20STATEMENT%20ON%20MANIPUR%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3EMANIPUR%20NEEDS%20THE%20HEALING%20TOUCH%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E6%20August%202023%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Constitutional%20Conduct%20Group%2C%20a%20group%20of%20former%20civil%20servants%20firmly%20committed%20to%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20and%20not%20affiliated%20to%20any%20political%20party%2C%20notes%20with%20the%20greatest%20concern%20the%20total%20breakdown%20of%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20constitutional%20values%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20since%20early%20May%202023.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20protest%20by%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20against%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Manipur%20High%20Court%2C%20directing%20the%20state%20government%20to%20recommend%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20the%20grant%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20to%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%2C%20has%20since%20snowballed%20into%20a%20dangerous%2C%20internecine%20ethnic%20conflict%20that%20threatens%20not%20just%20to%20tear%20apart%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20Manipur%20but%20calls%20into%20question%20the%20very%20spirit%20of%20harmony%20and%20fraternity%20that%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunity%20in%20diversity%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20wish%20to%20strongly%20highlight%20the%20dereliction%20of%20their%20fundamental%20duty%20by%20the%20Manipur%20state%20government%20and%20the%20state%20police%20in%20protecting%20the%20life%20and%20property%20of%20their%20citizens.%20This%20has%20created%20the%20conditions%20for%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20with%20a%20deliberately%20orchestrated%20and%20targeted%20carnage%20that%20has%20included%20large%20scale%20arson%2C%20lynching%2C%20collective%20rape%2C%20vandalism%2C%20looting%2C%20mob%20violence%20and%20obstruction%20of%20central%20security%20forces%20from%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties%2C%20followed%20by%20armed%20attacks%20and%20retaliation%20by%20both%20communities.%20These%20atrocities%20have%20taken%20place%20under%20a%20double-edged%20internet%20ban%2C%20lifted%20only%20partially%20on%20July%2025%2C%20that%20has%20prevented%20their%20horror%20and%20scale%20from%20coming%20out%20earlier%2C%20while%20also%20providing%20grist%20to%20rumour-mongering%20and%20spread%20of%20fake%20news.%C2%A0%20This%20total%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20has%20allowed%20the%20raiding%20of%20police%20armouries%20by%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20reportedly%20resulting%20in%20around%204%2C500%20weapons%20of%20varying%20sophistication%20and%20an%20estimated%205%20lakh%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%20being%20looted%2C%20which%20is%20continuing%20even%20to%20the%20present%20day.%20Such%20looting%20is%20unimaginable%20and%20without%20precedent%20anywhere%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20lends%20credence%20to%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr.%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20being%20partisan%20in%20his%20approach%20to%20tackling%20the%20tragedy%20is%20his%20demonisation%20and%20targeting%20of%20one%20community%20as%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eillegal%20migrants%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epoppy%20cultivators%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eencroachers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enarco-terrorists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eterrorists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99.%20These%20%E2%80%9Cdog%20whistles%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20smear%20an%20entire%20community%2C%20have%20served%20to%20excite%20the%20passions%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20to%20which%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20belongs.%20A%20high%20constitutional%20functionary%2C%20like%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20restore%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20cool%20inflamed%20passions%2C%20rather%20than%20stoke%20them%20further.%20The%20failure%20to%20take%20strong%20action%20against%20militant%20organisations%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%2C%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%2C%20which%20openly%20issue%20threats%20of%20%E2%80%9Cannihilation%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cblowing%20up%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20tribal%20Kuki-Zo%20minority%2C%20or%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20which%20advocates%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EManipuri%20national%20war%20against%20Chin-Kuki%20narco-terrorism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20arming%20of%20civilians%2C%20only%20seems%20to%20confirm%20fears%20about%20the%20partisan%20approach%20of%20the%20state%20administration%3B%20the%20same%20applies%20to%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20of%20Manipur%20state%20to%20the%20aggressive%20actions%20of%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%2C%20which%20include%20their%20preventing%20the%20army%20from%20apprehending%20those%20engaged%20in%20violent%20activities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20causes%20us%20even%20deeper%20anguish%2C%20as%20former%20civil%20servants%20who%20have%20dealt%20with%20surcharged%20law%20and%20order%20situations%20in%20the%20course%20of%20our%20careers%2C%20has%20been%20the%20largely%20passive%20role%20that%20the%20union%20government%20has%20played%20in%20this%20entire%20imbroglio.%20What%20was%20required%20at%20the%20very%20onset%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20May%202023%20was%20the%20imposition%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20given%20the%20abject%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20government%20to%20function%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20However%2C%20instead%20of%20invoking%20Article%20356%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20impose%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20a%20Security%20Adviser%20to%20the%20state%20and%20a%20new%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20from%20the%20cadre%20of%20a%20neighbouring%20state%20were%20appointed%2C%20and%20a%20Unified%20Command%20constituted%2C%20all%20reporting%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Apart%20from%20the%20visit%20to%20Manipur%20by%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20end%20May-early%20June%202023%2C%20when%20he%20met%20with%20different%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20active%20political%20involvement%20of%20the%20centre%20in%20establishing%20peace%20between%20the%20opposing%20communities.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20union%20government%20also%20lost%20a%20golden%20opportunity%20to%20involve%20the%20opposition%20parties%20in%20trying%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20political%20solution%20to%20the%20problem.%20Political%20expediency%20has%20won%20out%3A%20we%20are%20witness%20to%20the%20spectacle%20of%20a%20non-functioning%20parliament%20at%20a%20time%20of%20crisis%2C%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20making%20no%20statement%20in%20Parliament%20on%20the%20Manipur%20crisis%2C%20which%20would%20enable%20the%20initiation%20of%20a%20dialogue%20on%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20even%20more%20appalled%20at%20the%20approach%20of%20the%20union%20government%20to%20the%20ghastly%20events%20of%20the%20stripping%20and%20parading%20naked%20of%20two%20women%2C%20the%20alleged%20gangrape%20of%20one%20of%20them%20and%20the%20murder%20of%20two%20male%20members%2C%20all%20of%20the%20same%20family%2C%20on%20May%204.%20While%20expressing%20his%20outrage%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20outside%20Parliament%20rather%20than%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20either%20House%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20seemed%20to%20draw%20an%20equivalence%20between%20this%20incident%20in%20Manipur%20and%20other%20incidents%20in%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20though%20the%20incidents%20are%20not%20at%20all%20comparable.%20There%20was%20no%20explanation%20of%20how%20his%20government%20and%20the%20Manipur%20state%20government%20were%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20this%20heinous%20incident%20despite%20the%20filing%20of%20an%20FIR%20over%20two%20months%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20would%20like%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20union%20government%E2%80%99s%20notice%20that%20the%20May%204%20incident%20(along%20with%20other%20such%20similar%20incidents%20of%20sexual%20violence%20against%20women%20during%20the%20last%20three%20months%20in%20Manipur)%20represent%20the%20disgraceful%20phenomenon%20of%20Conflict%20Related%20Sexual%20Violence.%20The%20intent%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20this%20violence%20and%20their%20instigators%20is%20to%20use%20womens%E2%80%99%20bodies%20for%20signalling%20dominance.%20Failure%20to%20nip%20such%20perverted%20tendencies%20in%20the%20bud%20can%20lead%20to%20escalation%20in%20conflict%20and%20make%20reconciliation%20difficult.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Manipur%2C%20announced%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20panel%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20High%20Court%20judge%20to%20investigate%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20violence%20and%20to%20identify%20those%20behind%20the%20violence%2C%20this%20will%20not%20suffice%20to%20heal%20the%20wounds%20that%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20and%20the%20severe%20trust%20deficit%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20lack%20of%20confidence%20of%20the%20minority%20Kuki%20community%20in%20the%20impartial%20conduct%20of%20the%20state%20government%20and%20its%20police%20force.%20The%20nonpartisan%20and%20positive%20role%20played%20by%20the%20army%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20central%20paramilitary%20forces%2C%20which%20has%20been%20appreciated%2C%20indicates%20that%20there%20is%20need%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20deployment%20of%20these%20forces%20in%20the%20buffer%20zones%20between%20the%20two%20communities%2C%20to%20forestall%20offensive%20attacks%20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20immediate%20priority%20is%20to%20provide%20a%20healing%20touch%20to%20the%20affected%20persons%20of%20both%20communities.%20The%20lethargic%20relief%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20state%20government%20have%20been%20very%20inadequate.%20Effective%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20measures%20as%20well%20as%20adequate%20compensation%20need%20to%20be%20provided%20to%20all%20affected%20individuals%2Ffamilies%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives.%20These%20should%20include%3A%20(i)%20providing%20suitable%20shelters%20to%20the%20affected%2C%20either%20in%20public%20buildings%20or%20in%20requisitioned%20private%20premises%2C%20with%20proper%20hygiene%20and%20security%2C%20for%20as%20long%20as%20a%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20is%20not%20feasible%3B%20(ii)%20providing%20free%20food%20supplies%20for%20those%20in%20the%20relief%20camps%20and%20free%20PDS%20rations%20for%20internally%20displaced%20people%20residing%20elsewhere%20%3B%20(iii)%20starting%20MNREGA%20works%20that%20could%20provide%20income%20to%20those%20affected%3B%20(iv)%20providing%20childcare%2C%20health%2C%20trauma%20care%20and%20education%20services%20that%20would%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20those%20in%20the%20relief%20camps%2C%20especially%20mothers%20and%20children%2C%20including%20newborns%20(v)%20in%20the%20medium%20term%2C%20providing%20assistance%20for%20rebuilding%20damaged%20houses%20and%20other%20public%20premises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20u%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enderlying%20causes%20of%20the%20ongoing%20mayhem%20in%20Manipur%20need%20to%20be%20objectively%20identified%20and%20addressed%20within%20the%20bounds%20of%20constitutional%C2%A0parameters.%20Unsubstantiated%20charges%20and%20dangerous%20brinkmanship%20by%20all%20parties%2C%20and%20grave%20disruptions%20of%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20Manipur%2C%20as%20well%20as%20sustained%20violence%2C%20could%20resonate%20and%20spill%20over%20not%20only%20into%20neighbouring%20states%20but%20also%20across%20international%20borders%2C%20where%20ethnic%20bonds%20exist.%20This%20would%20be%20a%20recipe%20for%20unimaginable%20strife%20which%20will%20not%20leave%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20unscathed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20therefore%2C%20urge%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20take%20the%20following%20actions%20at%20the%20earliest%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1)%20Impose%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20Manipur%20and%20appoint%2C%20as%20Advisers%20to%20the%20Governor%2C%20experienced%20former%20administrators%20and%20police%20officers%20who%20have%20knowledge%20of%20the%20region%20and%20can%20empathetically%20interact%20with%20the%20local%20populace.%20Every%20effort%20should%20be%20made%20to%20restore%20the%20trust%20of%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20citizenry%20in%20the%20local%20administration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E2)%20Provide%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation%20measures%20as%20well%20as%20compensation%20to%20affected%20individuals%2Ffamilies%20in%20a%20nonpartisan%20manner%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20bringing%20back%20normalcy%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3)%20Take%20severe%20punitive%20action%20against%20individuals%20and%20groups%20intent%20on%20fomenting%20unrest%2C%20including%20bringing%20to%20justice%20all%20the%20instigators%20and%20perpetrators%20of%20incidents%20of%20violence%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20May%2C%20firmly%20checking%20hate%20speech%2C%20rounding%20up%20looted%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20and%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20offensive%20attacks%20against%20other%20communities.%20The%20message%20needs%20to%20firmly%20go%20out%20that%20no%20attempt%20by%20any%20non-state%20organisation%20to%20take%20the%20law%20into%20its%20hands%20will%20be%20tolerated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EWe%20earnestly%20entreat%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20as%20well%20as%20other%20stakeholders%20not%20to%20let%20issues%20of%20prestige%20and%20political%20expediency%20inform%20actions%2C%20when%20the%20imperatives%20of%20both%20internal%20peace%20and%20external%20security%20warrant%20mature%20responses.%20We%20must%20all%20realise%20that%20if%20India%20loses%2C%20no%20one%20wins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESATYAMEVA%20JAYATE%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConstitutional%20Conduct%20Group%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E(113%20signatories%2C%20as%20at%20pages%204-7%20below)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E1%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cspan%3EAnita%20Agnihotri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cspan%3EIAS%20(Retd.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20Secretary%2C%20Department%20of%20Social%20Justice%20Empowerment%2C%20GoI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E2%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%3C