3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095357%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.01-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Manipur%20Police%20has%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20personnel%20of%20the%209th%20battalion%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20for%20allegedly%20obstructing%20a%20public%20servant%20carrying%20out%20their%20duty%20and%20disobeying%20the%20law.%20The%20FIR%20pertains%20to%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20violence%20in%20Kwakta%2C%20Bishnupur%2C%20where%20three%20Meitei%20residents%20were%20killed%20on%20August%206.%20Two%20Kuki%20men%20were%20killed%20in%20retaliatory%20firing%20later%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Spear%20Corps%20said%20that%20there%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cfabricated%20attempts%E2%80%9D%20to%20malign%20the%20image%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fassam-rifles-kuki-militants-escape-manipur-police-fir-8882653%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20video%20of%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Bishnupur%20police%20had%20earlier%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen%2C%20alleges%20that%20Assam%20Rifles%20personnel%20blocked%20a%20road%20to%20Kwakta%2C%20not%20allowing%20the%20local%20police%20to%20make%20their%20way%20there.%20This%20%E2%80%9Carrogant%20act%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20FIR%20states%2C%20allowed%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20militants%E2%80%9D%20to%20escape%20after%20their%20attack%20before%20the%20police%20could%20get%20to%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kuki%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20have%20held%20the%20state%20government%20and%20police%20responsible%20for%20allowing%20violence%20against%20them%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20has%20faced%20anger%20in%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20Valley%20areas%20for%20allegedly%20supporting%20Kuki%20militant%20groups.%20The%20Manipur%20state%20unit%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20even%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20must%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20state%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20general%20public%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BJP%20unit%20demanded%20that%20they%20be%20replaced%20by%20%E2%80%9Cany%20other%20paramilitary%20forces%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Spear%20Corps%20said%20on%20Twitter%20that%20there%20have%20been%20fabricated%20attempts%20to%20malign%20the%20image%20of%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20inimical%20elements%20have%20made%20desperate%2C%20repeated%2C%20and%20failed%20attempts%20to%20question%20the%20role%2C%20intent%2C%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20Central%20security%20forces%2C%20especially%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20working%20relentlessly%20towards%20saving%20lives%20and%20restoration%20of%20peace%20in%20Manipur%20from%20May%203%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20said%20that%20due%20to%20the%20complex%20nature%20of%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Manipur%2C%20occasional%20differences%20at%20the%20tactical%20level%20do%20occur%20between%20various%20security%20forces.%20However%2C%20all%20such%20misunderstandings%20at%20the%20functional%20level%20are%20immediately%20addressed%20through%20the%20joint%20mechanism%20to%20synergise%20the%20efforts%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20normalcy%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20said%20two%20instances%20have%20emerged%20over%20the%20last%2024%20hours%20aimed%20at%20%E2%80%9Cmaligning%20the%20image%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20case%2C%20the%20Army%20said%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20battalion%20has%20acted%20strictly%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20Unified%20Headquarters%20of%20strict%20enforcement%20of%20buffer%20zone%20guidelines%20towards%20the%20aim%20of%20preventing%20violence%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20case%2C%20it%20said%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20being%20moved%20out%20of%20an%20area%20is%20not%20even%20related%20to%20them.%20%E2%80%9CAn%20infantry%20battalion%20of%20the%20Army%20is%20deployed%20in%20the%20area%2C%20since%20the%20crisis%20erupted%20in%20May%2C%20from%20where%20the%20narrative%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%20being%20moved%20out%20has%20been%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20Army%20and%20Assam%20Rifles%20assure%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20that%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20remain%20firm%20and%20resolute%20in%20our%20actions%20to%20prevent%20any%20attempt%20that%20could%20result%20in%20furthering%20violence%20in%20an%20already%20volatile%20atmosphere%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20Details%20from%20the%20statement%20by%20the%20Spear%20Corps%20was%20added%20to%20this%20story%20after%20it%20was%20published.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691558458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F09095357%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-08-at-12.03.01-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20of%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Bishnupur%20police%20had%20earlier%20gone%20viral.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20Agri-Tech%20Solution%20Helps%20Farmers%20Cut%20Water