2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20and%20Rahul%20met%20during%20their%20stint%20at%20Wayfair%2C%20an%20American%20e-commerce%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20EcoSoul%20was%20born%20out%20of%20our%20experiences%20at%20Wayfair.%20We%20were%20tasked%20with%20exploring%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20sustainable%20product%20category%20for%20the%20company.%20As%20we%20delved%20deeper%20into%20the%20sustainability%20space%20and%20analysed%20consumer%20behaviour%2C%20we%20noticed%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20eco-friendly%20alternatives.%20This%20realisation%20became%20our%20%3Cem%3Eaha%3C%2Fem%3E%20moment!%20We%20recognised%20that%20the%20market%20was%20ripe%20for%20disruption%20and%20that%20sustainable%20products%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20gain%20significant%20traction%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arvind%2C%20co-founder%2C%20EcoSoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20wave%20of%20transformation%20in%20consumer%20behaviour%20towards%20sustainability%20came%20in%20the%20food%20category.%20Today%2C%20many%20are%20consuming%20organic%2C%20unprocessed%20food.%20So%2C%20we%20figured%20the%20next%20breakout%20category%20had%20to%20be%20something%20that%20touches%20the%20food.%20For%20instance%2C%20your%20tabletop%20line%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20decided%20to%20sell.%20We%20wanted%20to%20disrupt%20this%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2040-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-founders%20quit%20their%20jobs%20in%20June%202020%2C%20right%20when%20COVID%20was%20beginning%20to%20rear%20its%20head%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20basically%20solving%20for%20the%20three%20big%20As%20%E2%80%94%20awareness%2C%20affordability%20and%20availability.%20Awareness%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20big%20problem%20as%20most%20people%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20plastic%20causes.%20We%20had%20to%20keep%20our%20prices%20within%2025%20percent%20of%20single-use%20plastic%20to%20make%20it%20affordable.%20The%20major%20challenge%20was%20availability%20as%20we%20started%20during%20COVID%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20make%20their%20products%20widely%20available%2C%20they%20had%20to%20work%20on%20a%20strong%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315625%2Fdelhi-meeta-sharma-gupta-shumee-sustainable-toy-brand-develop-cognitive-motor-skills-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%20game%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20massive%20supply%20chain%20can%20only%20be%20built%20out%20of%20Asia%2C%20for%20which%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20India.%20Another%20challenge%20was%20that%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20built%20sitting%20at%20home%2C%20which%20is%20where%20the%20world%20was%20in%202020.%20We%20slowly%20worked%20around%20it%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20strong%20supply%20chain%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Singh%2C%20Co-founder%20of%20EcoSoul%20Home%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115.jpeg%201066w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-500x750.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-768x1153.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Frahul-singh-1691067115-1023x1536.jpeg%201023w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%