3%2F08%2Fzankla-4-1690982206-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326128%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKirat%20with%20his%20team%20of%20artisans%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Zankla%20Studio%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20toys%2C%20Vibha%20Kamat%2C%20Neela%E2%80%99s%20daughter-in-law%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20toys%20really%20open%20up%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20for%20the%20children.%20My%20mother-in-law%E2%80%99s%20niece%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20why%20the%20doll%20was%20dressed%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20or%20where%20she%20is%20from.%20This%20introduced%20her%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20tribe%20and%20community%20that%20resides%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20future%20plans%2C%20Kirat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20hire%20more%20artisans%2C%20hence%20provide%20more%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20the%20people%20of%20my%20tribe.%20To%20me%2C%20this%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20business%3B%20it%20is%20my%20chance%20to%20add%20value%20to%20my%20community%20and%20showcase%20it%20to%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKirat%E2%80%99s%20toys%20are%20available%20for%20purchase%20on%20his%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zanklastudio.com%2Fshop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20his%20official%20Instagram%20handle%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzankla_studio%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40zankla_studio%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690983138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzan