%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dabbas%20are%20delivered%20on%20e-bikes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326062%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDabbas%20are%20delivered%20on%20e-bikes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283888%2Fdip-in-tiffin-dabba-by-srishti-garg-eco-friendly-packaging-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidea%20of%20DabbaDrop%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20experienced%20it.%20I%20loved%20the%20theatre%20of%20not%20knowing%20what%20was%20inside%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebefore%20I%20opened%20it%2C%20and%20the%20wholesome%20food%20and%20sustainability%20element%20really%20ticked%20all%20the%20boxes%20for%20me%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Renee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20issues%20we%20face%20in%20the%2021st%20century%20is%20the%20problem%20of%20plenty.%20We%20simply%20have%20too%20much%20choice.%20Anshu%20wanted%20to%20combat%20that%20through%20her%20humble%20%3Cem%3Edabbas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20in%20a%20world%20where%20we%20have%20to%20make%20so%20many%20choices%2C%20every%20single%20minute%20of%20the%20day.%20Our%20menus%20are%20set%20for%20the%20week.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20cho